  107. ‌let grow_stacks() =
  108.   let oldsize = env.stacksize in
  109.   let newsize = oldsize * 2 in
  110.   let new_s = Array.make newsize 0
  111.   and new_v = Array.make newsize (Obj.repr ())
  112.   and new_start = Array.make newsize dummy_pos
  113.   and new_end = Array.make newsize dummy_pos in
  114.     Array.blit env.s_stack 0 new_s 0 oldsize;
  115.     env.s_stack <- new_s;
  116.     Array.blit env.v_stack 0 new_v 0 oldsize;
  117.     env.v_stack <- new_v;
  118.     Array.blit env.symb_start_stack 0 new_start 0 oldsize;
  119.     env.symb_start_stack <- new_start;
  120.     Array.blit env.symb_end_stack 0 new_end 0 oldsize;
  121.     env.symb_end_stack <- new_end;
  122.     env.stacksize <- newsize

  130. let yyparse tables start lexer lexbuf =
  131.   let rec loop cmd arg =
  132.     match parse_engine tables env cmd arg with
  133.       Read_token ->
  134.         let t = Obj.repr(lexer lexbuf) in
  135.         env.symb_start <- lexbuf.lex_start_p;
  136.         env.symb_end <- lexbuf.lex_curr_p;
  137.         loop Token_read t
  138.     | Raise_parse_error ->
  139.         raise Parse_error
  140.     | Compute_semantic_action ->
  141.         let (action, value) =
  142.           try
  143.             (Semantic_action_computed, tables.actions.(env.rule_number) env)
  144.           with Parse_error ->
  145.             (Error_detected, Obj.repr ()) in
  146.         loop action value
  147.     | Grow_stacks_1 ->
  148.         grow_stacks(); loop Stacks_grown_1 (Obj.repr ())
  149.     | Grow_stacks_2 ->
  150.         grow_stacks(); loop Stacks_grown_2 (Obj.repr ())
  151.     | Call_error_function ->
  152.         tables.error_function "syntax error";
  153.         loop Error_detected (Obj.repr ()) in
  154. ‌  let init_asp = env.asp
  155.   and init_sp = env.sp

  158.   and init_curr_char = env.curr_char

  179.         current_lookahead_fun :=

  183.             else tables.transl_const.(Obj.magic tok) = curr_char);
  184.         raise exn

  186. ‌let peek_val env n =

  189. ‌let symbol_start_pos () =
  190.   let rec loop i =
  191.     if i <= 0 then env.symb_end_stack.(env.asp)
  192.     else begin
  193.       let st = env.symb_start_stack.(env.asp - i + 1) in
  194.       let en = env.symb_end_stack.(env.asp - i + 1) in
  195.       if st <> en then st else loop (i - 1)
  196.     end
  197.   in
  198.   loop env.rule_len

  200. ‌let symbol_end_pos () = env.symb_end_stack.(env.asp)
  201. ‌let rhs_start_pos n = env.symb_start_stack.(env.asp - (env.rule_len - n))
  202. ‌let rhs_end_pos n = env.symb_end_stack.(env.asp - (env.rule_len - n))

  204. ‌let symbol_start () = (symbol_start_pos ()).pos_cnum
